Is it possible to turn off the CAP policy and create a second policy with the same settings to see if the issue repeats?
The issue repeats after turning off the CAP policy and create a second one with the same settings.
Even though it remains only one CAP policy, it cannot generate any logs for changes in the ‘Reports and Analysis > Admin Actions’ – it just turns on / off in ‘Status’.
